{"tid":785441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友嘅選擇","createTime":"2018-08-19T08:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T12:31:39.000Z","uid":43141,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a57907d745db05448ad1ca0f2725f41fbd71935","tid":785441,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"朋友做左十幾年野，無生仔，辭左份工<br />\n兩個搬左去離島，平租，少欲知足，無乜錢洗，係島上打份hea pt，一星期出兩日省城，又做吓以前無諗過做嘅工，例如籃球教練<br />\n自娛力高，日日健康自煮，做運動，放狗，種花，行沙灘，睇日落，睇書<br />\n離島好遠？<br />\n慢船去中環唔洗一個鐘，永遠唔會塞車。<br />\n校啱時間銅鑼灣返到屋企唔洗個半鐘<br />\n當然永遠有利有弊，只係佢嘅另類選擇，可以聽吓"},{"pid":"83c5a3ad5796f0ba9e9a4725aeac2639839b33dc","tid":785441,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"好想住南丫/坪洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5065bd9d1f87b39d1fe5f6baf531abf6897534b3","tid":785441,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"坪洲正<br />\n不過船費要22"},{"pid":"eb58eefc3e1988d425fd30ed1173136fea3ae16d","tid":785441,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"佢話反而最慘係要飛，要兜大圈"},{"pid":"6a0d21b534ea5b1949d3d1c8fc9d1381c4b11124","tid":785441,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔大病冇意外就好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b8a2430c8e2ed20a5c1ff96930ed58884e72fb","tid":785441,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0d21b534ea5b1949d3d1c8fc9d1381c4b11124","tid":785441,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔大病冇意外就好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-